---
title: Caribbean Chicken & Pineapple Tacos with Slaw & Peanuts
description: A summer time fave, is being whipped up tonight. Chicken tacos that are glazed and topped with a bursting sweetcorn salsa.
Go crazy and add a sprinkling of peanuts to enjoy these warmer nights.
